Text: this recording would not be 1973 because he died 1973. This would be pre Allman Brothers Band, approx. 1964

This would probably be February, March or April of 1966. ABB was formed 3/1969 and Duane died 11/29/1971. This could be the Dial Records Sessions or some studio cuts laid down in April, 1966. I have not listened to it yet. FYI
